  @TechnicalDesign_540c028e = N'Loads all invoices for current year via RunView. Adds computed Month and MonthName fields to each invoice record. Passes detail records to SimpleDrilldownChart which performs client-side aggregation by month and sums TotalAmount. Uses bar chart for time series. Grid shows invoice details with standard invoice fields.'
